<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٦٣٦ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى:</span> حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ الْأَعْلَى: حَدَّثَنَا خَالِدٌ، عَنْ عِكْرِمَةَ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٦١٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">عَنِ ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ <span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">سُئِلَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فَقَالَ:</span> رَمَيْتُ بَعْدَمَا أَمْسَيْتُ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(لَا حَرَجَ)</span>.<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> حَلَقْتُ قَبْلَ أَنْ أَنْحَرَ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(لَا حَرَجَ)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
